{"unit_id":"3c79e138-923d-4606-8d02-24b8ce2f0afb.00007.paragraph.c797bcbe.sentence.0","openstax_book_id":"06aba565-9432-40f6-97ee-b8a361f118a8","revision":"ee086d3","slug":"2-keyterms","page_title":"Key Terms","chapter_number":2,"chapter_title":"Chapter 2 Psychological Research","unit_type":"paragraph","source_text":"serves as a basis for comparison and controls for chance factors that might influence the results of the study—by holding such factors constant across groups so that the experimental manipulation is the only difference between groups","source_lang":"eng_Latn","mt_text":"ጥናቱን ውጤቶች ላይ ተጽዕኖ ሊያሳድሩ የሚችሉ የአጋጣሚ ምክንያቶችን ለማወዳደር እና ለመቆጣጠር መሠረት ሆኖ ያገለግላል","mt_lang":"amh_Ethi","pe_text":"የጥናቱን ውጤቶች የሚቀይሩ በአጋጣሚ የሚከሰቱ ነገሮችን ለማወዳደርና ለመቆጣጠር እንደ መሰረት ሁኖ ያገለግላል። እነዚህን ነገሮች በቡድኖች መካከል ቋሚ በማድረግ በሙከራ የሚደረግ መቆጣጠር ወይም ለውጥ ብቻ ይሆናል ልዩነታቸው።","edited":true}
