{"unit_id":"3c79e138-923d-4606-8d02-24b8ce2f0afb.00007.paragraph.c797bcbe.sentence.0","openstax_book_id":"06aba565-9432-40f6-97ee-b8a361f118a8","revision":"ee086d3","slug":"2-keyterms","page_title":"Key Terms","chapter_number":2,"chapter_title":"Chapter 2 Psychological Research","unit_type":"paragraph","source_text":"relationship between two or more variables; when two variables are correlated, one variable changes as the other does","source_lang":"eng_Latn","mt_text":"በሁለት ወይም ከዚያ በላይ ተለዋዋጮች መካከል ያለው ግንኙነት፤ ሁለት ተለዋዋጮች ሲዛመዱ አንደኛው ተለዋዋጭ ከሌላው ጋር ሲነፃፀር ይለወጣል","mt_lang":"amh_Ethi","pe_text":"በሁለት ወይም ከዚያ በላይ ተለዋዋጮች መካከል ያለ ግንኙነት፤ ሁለት ተለዋዋጮች በመተያየብ (correlated) ሲሆኑ አንዱ ተለዋዋጭ ሲለወጥ ሌላውም እንደዚያው ይለወጣል።","edited":true}
